@startuml UC_20_Private_Messaging
title UC-20: Private Messaging

|User|
start
:(1) Open Messages;

|System|
:(2) Load the user's channels and recent messages;
:(3) Return the conversation list;

|User|
:(4) Select a conversation;
:(5) Type a message and send it;

|System|
:(6) Validate channel membership and recipient settings;
:(7) Persist the message;
:(8) Broadcast the message to the conversation members;
:(9) Mark the channel as read for the current user;
:(10) Return delivery status;

stop
@enduml
